{
  "stem": "20021.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "See, forged in the sense that my identity card was obtained under false pretenses, but it was not forged.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was issued in a genuine way by the police.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The other one was totally forged.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I just bought it from forgers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now, the two apartments helped for two reasons.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "A, if for some reason I would be compromised or caught and managed still to escape with my life, I couldn't go back to this apartment, because as they caught me, they identified my address.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I would have at least where to sleep the next night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But two, even more importantly was where I lived I pretended that I am actually a resident in Lwow.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I'm only in Warsaw on business.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the other apartment, I pretended the same story.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But as I moved from this apartment, I moved into the other apartment, and back and forth in that way.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You know, I kept-- and I kept myself busy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Every day I would leave the house in the morning, and come back at night.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I had to spend the whole day someplace in the city, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Lots of hours I would spend in the tramway, which is a bus, a public bus.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But, you know, electrical-driven car, a trolley car.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the trolleys were packed full.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So it was safe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You know, you couldn't talk to anybody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Because you were that packed up, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Or you could ask maybe a question.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But you couldn't carry on a conversation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I would go to movies very often, and spend hours in movies, but always enter when it's dark, and try to leave before the lights came on.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then go back to another movie, and do the same thing.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
